# --- COMMIT END ---
# Type can be:
#   mobile   - Mobile app changes (Flutter)
#   web      - Web frontend changes (React)
#   backend  - Backend service changes (Node.js/Express)
#   shared   - Shared resources across platforms
#   all      - Changes affecting all platforms
#   docs     - Documentation only
#   ci       - CI/CD configuration
#   test     - Adding or updating tests
#   refactor - Code refactoring
#   fix      - Bug fix
#   feat     - New feature
#   chore    - Build process or auxiliary tool changes
# --------------------
# Scope examples (optional):
#   mobile(ui)     - UI changes in mobile app
#   mobile(db)     - Database changes in mobile app
#   web(style)     - Styling changes in web app
#   backend(api)   - API changes in backend
#   backend(db)    - Database changes in backend
# --------------------
# Example commits:
#   mobile: add word list page
#   mobile(ui): implement learning mode interface
#   mobile(db): setup drift database schema
#   web: update word card component
#   web(style): improve mobile responsive design
#   backend: add quiz generation endpoint
#   backend(api): optimize exercise generation
#   shared: add new vocabulary templates
#   all: update project dependencies
#   docs: update architecture diagram
#   ci: add flutter build workflow
